{
  "texts": [
    "When dynamic security policies are required, reinforcement learning (RL) with a focus on Q-learning provides an attractive approach to intrusion detection.",
    "Since cybercriminals are always coming up with new ways to circumvent security measures, the landscape of network protection is anything from stable.",
    "Q-learning excels in this setting.",
    "Using this method of reinforcement learning, security experts may teach agents to take precautions that will have the greatest long-term impact 39.",
    "The optimal responses to network threats can be defined and rewarded in this way."
  ]
}